videos.headline: Georgia nabs Louisiana Lafayette interception
videos.description: Georgia Bulldog DeAndre Baker leaps for an early interception against the Rajun Cajuns.

videos.headline: Georgia's McKenzie returns punt to the house for TD
videos.description: Georgia's Isaiah McKenzie flexes his athleticism up the field as he returns Louisiana Lafayette's punt to the house for his second TD of the game.

videos.headline: Bulldogs' Davis picks it off, as Jennings throws second interception of game
videos.description: Anthony Jennings pass intercepted Aaron Davis return for a loss of 8 yards to the Geo 8

videos.headline: Cajuns' Walker makes the pick off deflection
videos.description: Jacob Eason pass intercepted Tracy Walker return for 39-yards to the Geo 47

videos.headline: Lafayette QB loses ball after hard hit, Georgia recovers
videos.description: Dion Ray run for 2-yards to the LaLaf 45 Dion Ray fumbled, forced by Aaron Davis, recovered by Geo Lorenzo Carter

videos.headline: Eason finds TE Nauta in back of end zone for six
videos.description: Jacob Eason pass complete to Isaac Nauta for 9-yards for a TD

videos.headline: Jennings scramble puts the Cajuns on the board
videos.description: Anthony Jennings run for 9 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Jennings hits streaking Riles in slot for 64-yard pick up
videos.description: Anthony Jennings pass complete to Al Riles for 64-yards to the Geo 9 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Bulldogs Parrish makes leaping interception grab
videos.description: Anthony Jennings pass intercepted Malkom Parrish return for a loss of 5-yards to the Geo 25. Jennings throws third interception of game.

videos.headline: Nick Chubb goes over the top for the score
videos.description: Nick Chubb dives over the Lafayette line and extends the ball for the rushing TD.

videos.headline: No catching Chubb on 49-yard TD reception
videos.description: Nick Chubb isn't known for making many catches, but when he's left wide open in the middle of the field, he makes the grab and then goes the rest of the way for a 49-yard touchdown in Georgia's win.

videos.headline: Cajun QB Jennings keeps it for second score of game
videos.description: Anthony Jennings run for 13-yards for a TD

videos.headline: Cajun WR Fuselier makes slick sliding catch
videos.description: Anthony Jennings pass complete to Gabe Fuselier for 24-yards to the Geo 1 for a 1ST down. Call on field confirmed after review.

videos.headline: Jennings keeps it for third score of game
videos.description: Anthony Jennings run for 1-yard for a TD (Stevie Artigue KICK)
